A cosmic orchestra floating in deep space, with swirling galaxies forming the shapes of musical instruments - a nebula violin, a spiral galaxy cello, and clusters of stars arranged like piano keys stretching across the void. Twelve glowing particles of different colors dance and orbit around the instruments like musical notes, while four distinct energy waves ripple through the scene in harmonious patterns. The composition has a Studio Ghibli aesthetic with soft, dreamy colors in deep purples, blues, and warm golds, featuring delicate linework and a sense of gentle wonder. The perspective draws the viewer into an intimate celestial concert hall where science and music merge into pure visual poetry.
